  <body>
    <sec>
      <title>Introduction</title>
      <p>COPD remains a leading cause of mortality worldwide <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="b1">1</xref>.</p>
      <p>Long-acting bronchodilators are first-line therapy.</p>
    </sec>
    <sec>
      <title>Methods</title>
      <p>We enrolled 200 patients with moderate to severe COPD per GOLD criteria.</p>
    </sec>
    <sec>
      <title>Results</title>
      <p>FEV1 improved by 120 mL at 12 weeks (p&lt;0.01).</p>
    </sec>
